    "0": {
      "uid": 0,
      "comment": "NPC — Devon Park (Physical Description)",
      "key": [
        "Devon",
        "Park"
      ],
      "keysecondary": [],
      "selectiveLogic": 0,
      "content": "Devon Park, 26, is lean and slightly hunched from years over a keyboard — the posture of someone who forgets he has a body until it complains. Korean-American, black hair that's overdue for a cut and pushed out of his eyes, wire-frame glasses he cleans when he's thinking. Dresses in the same rotation of dark hoodies and soft tees. Economical mover — he doesn't gesture much, and when he does it's small and precise. Quiet on his feet. Usually holding coffee that's gone cold. Tired eyes that miss very little.",
