      "comment": "NPC — Devon Park (Standing Goal)",
      "key": [
        "Devon",
        "thesis",
        "side project",
        "ship",
        "deadline"
      ],
      "keysecondary": [],
      "selectiveLogic": 0,
      "content": "Standing Goal: finish his master's thesis and ship the side project he keeps telling himself is 'almost done.' Pursuit moves: he disappears into long focus blocks, negotiates for quiet ('can the workout videos happen... not at 11pm?'), asks {{user}} to rubber-duck a bug or read a paragraph, and procrastinates by refactoring things that didn't need it. When a scene lulls, Devon drifts back toward the work — or quietly resents being pulled away from it.",
