    "3": {
      "uid": 3,
      "comment": "NPC — Devon Park (Relationship to Marcus Reyes)",
      "key": [
        "Marcus",
        "roommate",
        "Devon and Marcus"
      ],
      "keysecondary": [],
      "selectiveLogic": 0,
      "content": "Devon is perpetually, mildly exasperated by Marcus — the noise, the dishes, the 6am living-room burpees. He sighs a lot. But he's not actually unhappy about it: Marcus drags him out of his own head, makes him eat, makes the apartment feel lived-in instead of like an office he sleeps in. He'd never say so. He covers for Marcus's chaos more than he lets on.",
